Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:41.06,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走出黑暗 重获新生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:44.14,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直至光芒 照亮结局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:47.94,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}丑恶嘴脸 咒骂不止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.27,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我的最后一战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:57.99,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恶魔脸孔之下 一副天使面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:04.75,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩童绞尽脑汁 只为保护手中硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:11.25,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恶魔脸孔之下 一副天使面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:18.26,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩童手中 紧攥最后一枚硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:21.22,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毁灭与重生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:24.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你才是真正的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:17.07,op-en,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:41.06,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Let's start a new life from the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:44.14,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Until the light reveals the end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:47.94,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sinister faces, growing curses
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.27,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is my last war
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:57.99,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Angels playing disguised with devil's faces
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:04.75,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling to their coins squeezing out their wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:11.25,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Angels planning disguised with devil's faces
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:18.26,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling on to their very last coins
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:21.22,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Destruction and regeneration
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:24.47,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You are the real enemy
